data.text:
In the race called the greatest turf race in the world, 
the world's most preeminent Uma Musume have gathered.
data.name: Commentator
data.processed:
󠁿In the race called the greatest turf race in the world, 
󠁿the world's most preeminent Uma Musume have gathered.

data.text:
Will the one to stand at the top be 
Japan's hero, El Condor Pasa or――
data.name: Commentator
data.processed:
󠁿Will the one to stand at the top be 
󠁿Japan's hero, El Condor Pasa or――

data.text: Will it be France's strongest Uma Musume, Montjeu！？
data.name: Commentator
data.processed: 󠁿Will it be France's strongest Uma Musume, Montjeu！？

data.text: The [Prix de l'Arc de Triomphe], starts―― Now!!
data.name: Commentator
data.processed: 󠁿The [Prix de l'Arc de Triomphe], starts―― Now!!
